    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wojak Rush: Simple Rules, Complex Challenges!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rule #1:</strong> Be a Wojak. <strong>Rule #2:</strong> Avoid the traps. Sounds easy, right? Think again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to face a relentless gauntlet of irksome challenges and treacherous terrains designed to test your reflexes and patience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can You Handle the Pressure?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stay Cool… or Don’t, and Die!</strong><br>Your nerves will be pushed to the limit. Lose focus for a moment, and it’s game over.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reflexes Put to the Test!</strong><br>Every trap is designed to catch you off guard. Can you stay one step ahead?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Troll Background Music:</strong><br>The soundtrack will mock your failures, adding an extra layer of frustration and hilarity.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Journey of Pain and Progress</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expect to Fail—A Lot:</strong><br>Death is inevitable, and with every failure, you lose all your progress. But each attempt makes you better, sharper, and more determined.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Symphony of Ragdoll Deaths:</strong><br>Experience a variety of hilarious and sometimes infuriating death animations, thanks to the game’s ragdoll physics.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Ultimate Reward</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hidden Treasure Awaits:</strong><br>Endure the torment, outwit the traps, and claim the ultimate prize. Nothing beats the satisfaction of overcoming every obstacle in your path.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you be the Wojak who masters every level, conquers frustration, and finishes with the least deaths in the shortest time?</strong> Prove it!</p>",
